A cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da kuma a cikin United Kingdom, adadin cututtukan cutar COVID-19 sun karu da sauri tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Kasashen da ke cikin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da na Burtaniya suna nuna irin wannan yanayin na cutar ta Coronavirus (COVID-19) wanda ya tabbatar da cewa ko da yake matakan sun bambanta daga ƙasa zuwa ƙasa, cutar COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, dole ne kasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya su kara shirye-shiryen su don karuwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19, waɗanda za su bukaci kula da lafiya da musamman, magani mai inganci.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019, an gano jerin cututtukan cutar huhu na asibiti da ba a san su ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar China ta ba da shawarar sabon coronavirus a matsayin matsakaiciyar hanyar cutar, wanda yanzu ake kira cutar ta hanyar numfashi mai tsanani ta SARS-CoV-2 (SARS-CoV-2).
An kira shi cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) saboda cutar ta samo asali ne daga kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Shaidar da aka samu ta nuna cewa kashi 80 cikin dari na mutanen da ke fama da COVID-19 suna da cututtuka masu laushi, wato, kamuwa da cutar huhu tare da ko ba tare da cutar ba, kuma yawancin sun warke.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin 100 na shari'o'in COVID-19 ya zama mafi tsanani wanda ya bukaci a kwantar da shi asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin 100 na shari'o'in ya zama mafi tsanani wanda ke buƙatar zurfin magani.
Yawan mutuwar da aka yi a asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4 cikin 100.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin yanayin yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin EU/EEA da kuma a cikin United Kingdom (UK) kuma muka kwatanta su da lardin Hubei na China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin adadin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK da waɗanda suka kamu da cutar tsakanin 31 ga Janairu - 15 ga Maris, 2020 a cikin Italiya.
Kasashen EU/EEA da UK sun kamu da cutar COVID-19
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwa a cikin yanayin ƙasa, kuma a sauran duniya, bayanan annobar COVID-19 yanzu suna bin halin da kasar ke ciki.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin wata sanarwa da aka fitar a ranar 5 ga watan Maris na EuroSurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al, an ba da rahoton farkon lamarin COVID-19 a Turai, a cewar ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da sanarwar farko na mutum uku da suka dawo daga Wuhan, Hubei, China, a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an sami shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU/EEA 30 da United Kingdom (UK), tare da adadin shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, tare da mutuwar 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da kuma samun adadin shari'o'in COVID-19
Cibiyar Tarayyar Turai don Rigakafin Cututtuka da Kulawa (ECDC) tana yin rikodin shari'o'in COVID-19 na kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda ake sabuntawa kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe ta amfani da ma'aikatun lafiya na ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da ƙasa da na yanki da kuma WHO ta hanyar amfani da tushen hukuma.
Ana amfani da wannan bayanan ne don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta su da shari'o'in da aka samu a Italiya.
A matsayin samfurin yawan adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 masu aiki, mun lissafa adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 na kwanaki 14 a cikin yanayin da ya dace, yana la'akari da yaduwar COVID-19 a cikin kowace EU/EEA da Burtaniya tsakanin 1 ga Janairu - 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da jimlar adadin wadanda aka samu a kowace kasa da misalin karfe 8:00 na safe a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 kuma mun kwatanta su da wadanda aka samu a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Halin da ake samu na COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Halin da ake ciki na yau da kullum na COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK yana kama da na lardin Hubei (China) (Figure 1).
A cikin EU/EEA gabaɗaya, da kuma a cikin Burtaniya, an fara samun karuwar adadin COVID-19 a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan ya fara karuwa cikin sauri har zuwa 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (ƙarin abun ciki).
Wannan ya ƙunshi yawan adadin wadanda aka samu a cikin Italiya, amma ya nuna cewa akwai karuwar adadin COVID-19 a duk sauran kasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya (ƙarin bayani).
Hoton 2 ya nuna jimlar adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK, idan aka kwatanta da wadanda aka samu a Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya kuma nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga watan Maris da karfe 8 na safe, an riga an samu adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar a Italiya, kamar yadda aka samu a sauran kasashe 15 na EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya, makonni uku kafin wannan lokaci.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa, a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya, adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 yana ƙaruwa sosai.
