Bugu da kari, yayin da kasashe daban-daban ke cikin matakai daban-daban, dole ne a bincika bambancin dake tsakanin amsoshin lafiyar jama'a na kasa da kuma yiwuwar tantancewar shari'o'i daban-daban a tsakanin kasashe da kuma hanyoyin daban-daban na zaɓar marasa lafiya don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin kamawa.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 ke bukatar maganin wuce gona da iri, kuma kafofin yada labarai sun nuna cewa asibitoci da cibiyoyin maganin wuce gona da iri a wadannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar iyawarsu.
Bayanai game da shigar da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a asibitoci da/ko cibiyoyin kula da cututtuka a halin yanzu suna samuwa ne kawai ga 6% da 1% na shari'o'in a matakin EU/EEA, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
