Wannan yana nufin cewa sauran ƙasashe suna da albarkatu da yawa ko ƙasa da Italiya (da 12.5 na hypermedical da Mediummedical beds a kowace yawan mutane 100,000 a 2010-11).
Ana samun karuwar shari'o'in COVID-19 a asibitoci a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya. Wannan yanayin samfurin da ke tattare da saturatedness na iyawar HealthNigation yana da alaƙa da haɗarin wucewa > 90% na ƙarfin kwanciyar hankali na ICTs, wanda aka bayar a cikin sabuntawa ta shida na ECDC Rapid Risk Assessment na COVID-19.
