Cutar Corona Virus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) ta barke ne saboda cutar ta Coronavirus (SARS) mai tsanani ta Coronavirus (SARS-CoV-2) wanda ya haifar da mutuwar mutane sama da 3,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, kuma ya kamu da mutane sama da 80,000, wanda ya zama bala'i ga bil'adama.
Kamar SARS-CoV-2 wanda ya haifar da cutar SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da dubban mutane a shekara ta 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar cututtukan fata kuma yana nuna alamun bayyanar cututtuka ta hanyar fasaha iri ɗaya.
Ko da yake, cutar COVID-19 tana da ƙarancin tsanani da mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma ana samun karuwar kamuwa da ita a cikin tsofaffi fiye da matasa da kuma a cikin maza fiye da mata.
A cikin amsa ga yawan wallafe-wallafen da ke faruwa game da cutar, wannan labarin yana ƙoƙarin samar da cikakken bayani game da batun bincike da ke faruwa a cikin lokaci mai dacewa.
Mun yi amfani da ilimin cututtuka, ilimin halayyar mutum, ilimin cutar, bincike, magani, annobar cutar, da kuma rigakafin cutar.
Ko da yake har yanzu akwai amsoshin tambayoyi da yawa, muna fatan wannan bita zai taimaka mana mu fahimci wannan mummunar cuta kuma mu magance ta.
Ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ta kasance abin tunawa ga dukan mutanen kasar Sin da aka ce su zauna a gida a lokacin hutu da kuma makonni masu zuwa saboda barkewar sabuwar cuta.
Wannan cutar ta kasance mai kama da cutar coronavirus (CoV), wanda ya haifar da cutar ta SARS mai tsanani a shekara ta 2003, saboda haka a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, WHO ta sake suna da SARS-CoV-2 da kuma cutar da ta danganci shi da sunan COVID-19.
Cutar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin, kuma nan da nan ta bazu zuwa dukan kasar da kuma sauran kasashe 50 a duniya.
