Yawancin cututtukan sun kasance a cikin kasuwancin sayar da abincin teku na Hunan, saboda haka ana ganin cewa kwayar cutar ta samo asali ne daga dabbobi.
Wannan sabon kwayar cutar da aka gano da ke haifar da cutar ta SARS-CoV-2 tana da alaƙa da cutar Corona na fuka-fuki, cutar Corona ta cats da aka ci da SARS-CoV. An gano cewa mutumin da aka sani da farko da ya fara samun alamun cutar ya kamu da cutar a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma ba shi da alaƙa kai tsaye da rukunin kasuwar taro na baya.
A cikin rukunin farkon shari'o'in da aka samu a shekarar 2019, kashi biyu bisa uku na shari'o'in da aka samu sun danganta ga kasuwa.
Rahoton da ba a tabbatar ba na Morning Post na Kudancin China a ranar 13 ga Maris, 2020 ya nuna cewa wannan na iya zama farkon shari'ar mutum mai shekaru 55 a lardin Hubei wanda aka lura da shi zuwa 17 ga Nuwamba, 2019. A ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, 2020, WHO ta ba da rahoton cewa yayin da sabbin shari'o'in suka ragu a China amma suka karu a Italiya da Koriya ta Kudu, adadin sabbin shari'o'in da aka samu a waje da China ya karu fiye da na kasar Sin a karon farko.
Ana iya samun rahotanni da yawa a cikin ƙananan bayanai, musamman ma a cikin waɗanda suka nuna alamun rashin lafiya.
A ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, an samu karamin adadin shari'o'i a tsakanin matasa, wadanda shekarunsu 19 ko ƙasa da haka sun kai kashi 2.4% na shari'o'in a duniya. Patrick Valance, babban mai ba da shawara kan likitancin Burtaniya, ya kiyasta cewa kashi 60% na yawan mutanen Burtaniya suna bukatar kamuwa da cutar kafin su sami rigakafin gaba daya.
