Iran ta fara samun mutum na farko da aka tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 19 ga Fabrairu a Com, inda ta samu mutuwar a ranar, a cewar ma'aikatar kiwon lafiya da ilimin likitanci.
