B'angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne wanda ke haɗe da farfajiya (ƙungiyoyin ƙwayoyin cuta) na ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda da hanji.
Ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin -II da kuma ƙara adadin Ang1 -7) yana hana aikin ACE2 na ƙwayoyin cuta na angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE), kuma saboda haka yana da tabbacin magani don magance cututtukan zuciya da jijiyoyin jini. ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin hanyar shiga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta don wasu ƙwayoyin cuta.
Ana kiran wannan adadi na mutum hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 shine zinc-containing metallol-enzyme wanda yake a saman endothelial da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Protein ACE2 yana da wani N-terminal peptide M2 domain da kuma C-terminal colectrain renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 wani furotin ne na fata mai ƙyama wanda ke aiki ta hanyar aikinsa a saman ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin huhu da sauran ƙwayoyin cuta.
Ƙarin ƙwayoyin halitta na ACE2 ana cire su daga wani ƙwayar cuta mai suna shades, wanda ke haifar da sakin furotin mai narkewa cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe ya narke cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin dukkan gabobin jiki: yana da alaƙa da ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar cuta na nau'in II a cikin huhu, ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin ƙananan hanji, ƙwayoyin cuta na jijiyoyin jini da jijiyoyin jini, da kuma ƙwayoyin jijiyoyin jijiyoyin jiki a cikin gabobin jiki.
Ana samun ACE2 mRNA a cikin ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwa, stratoma, hypothalamus, da kuma brainstorm.
Yin aiki a matsayin mai tsayayya da ACE2 shine babban aikin ACE2.
ACE angiotensin I yana ba da izinin shiga cikin vascoconstricting angiotensin II.
A maimakon haka, ACE2 yana karɓar amino acid mai carboxylic-terminal daga anjiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma yana hydrolyzing shi zuwa vasodilator anjiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
[des-Arg9]- ACE2 na iya karya wasu wasu peptides da suka hada da bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana sarrafa ƙwayar ƙwayar ƙwayar cuta na SLC6A19, mai ɗaukar amino acid mai tsaka tsaki, kuma yana cikin cututtukan zuciya.
A matsayin furotin mai canzawa, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban hanyar shiga cikin kwayoyin halitta don wasu ƙwayoyin corona, gami da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (wanda ke haifar da SARS); da kuma SARS-CoV-2 (wanda ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, an yi amfani da endocytosis don ɗaure ƙwayoyin ACE2 na enzymatic domain zuwa saman sel ta hanyar SARS-CoV da kuma spike S1 na SARS-CoV2 zuwa endocytosis, kuma ana yin amfani da duka ƙwayoyin cuta da enzyme a cikin endosomes da ke cikin sel.
Don samun damar shiga, TMPRSS2 mai ba da sabis na sirrin na kuma buƙatar yin amfani da furotin S, wanda ake hanawa a cikin binciken da ake yi a yanzu a matsayin magani mai yiwuwa. Saboda haka, wasu sun kammala cewa rage matakan ACE2 a cikin ƙwayoyin zai taimaka wajen yaki da kamuwa da cuta.
Koyaya, yawancin kungiyoyi masu sana'a da hukumomi sun ba da shawarar ci gaba da maganin ACE mai hanawa da ARB.
